00:35:14,360 --> 00:35:17,560
Been out with that Feytek boy again?

552
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:19,200
Sasha.

553
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:21,260
You may

554
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,730
Look like me...

