00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:26,130
But you take after your
mom when it comes to boys,

556
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:27,700
Now, don't you?

557
00:35:27,730 --> 00:35:29,860
Hopefully, with a little better taste.

558
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:36,160
Damn it, girl, you are
gonna show me some respect.

559
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:52,030
<i>I know Sara didn't have many friends.</i>

