00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:11,760
This is the only thing I could think of.

649
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:17,500
I swore I'd leave you alone,
but I had to contact you.

650
00:40:17,530 --> 00:40:20,230
Because I have something?

